<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 06:10:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>真主党试图阻止以色列入侵加沙，北部紧张局势加剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/tensions-rise-in-the-north-as-hezbollah-tries-to-deter-israel-from-invading-gaza/0000018b-34d8-ddcb-a7bf-b7db6f590000</link><description>真主党正在以牙还牙，考验以色列的耐心，重点关注以色列在加沙地带的下一步行动。尽管如此，这并不是现状，而且存在相当大的误判风险</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 05:33:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/tensions-rise-in-the-north-as-hezbollah-tries-to-deter-israel-from-invading-gaza/0000018b-34d8-ddcb-a7bf-b7db6f590000</guid></item><item><title>报道：以色列同意加沙南部临时停火，拉法过境点将开放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article-live/israel-prepares-for-ground-invasion-biden-big-mistake-to-reoccupy-gaza/0000018b-364f-dc99-a1db-3fcf1ae10000</link><description>黎巴嫩报道：美国向哈马斯提供援助，以释放人质 ■ 埃及消息人士称，以色列同意暂时停火，拉法过境点即将开放 ■ 加沙火箭弹 10 小时内首次向以色列发射 ■ 自哈马斯袭击以来，已有 1,300 多名以色列人丧生，至少 2,600 名加沙人丧生</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 05:22:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article-live/israel-prepares-for-ground-invasion-biden-big-mistake-to-reoccupy-gaza/0000018b-364f-dc99-a1db-3fcf1ae10000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对巴勒斯坦裔美国男孩被谋杀感到“恶心”：“可怕的仇恨行为”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/biden-sickened-over-palestinian-american-boys-murder-horrific-act-of-hate/0000018b-365a-da5e-abef-bf7f485a0000</link><description>以色列和加沙战争期间，一名 6 岁儿童因伊斯兰教信仰在伊利诺伊州遭到袭击，被刺死，他的母亲受伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 02:54:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/biden-sickened-over-palestinian-american-boys-murder-horrific-act-of-hate/0000018b-365a-da5e-abef-bf7f485a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府各部委的崩溃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-16/ty-article-opinion/the-collapse-of-government-ministries/0000018b-34b4-dc80-a1ef-fff4fa900000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 02:22:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-16/ty-article-opinion/the-collapse-of-government-ministries/0000018b-34b4-dc80-a1ef-fff4fa900000</guid></item><item><title>德国，你早已背叛了你的责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/germany-you-have-long-since-betrayed-your-responsibility/0000018b-3487-d051-a1cb-3ddfa2cf0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 02:21:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/germany-you-have-long-since-betrayed-your-responsibility/0000018b-3487-d051-a1cb-3ddfa2cf0000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙，地狱之门已敞开</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-gaza-the-gates-of-hell-have-been-thrown-wide-open/0000018b-3487-d051-a1cb-3ddfa3d70000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 02:01:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-gaza-the-gates-of-hell-have-been-thrown-wide-open/0000018b-3487-d051-a1cb-3ddfa3d70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列地面入侵迫在眉睫 拜登：重新占领加沙将是一个大错误</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/biden-as-israels-ground-invasion-looms-it-would-be-a-mistake-to-reoccupy-gaza/0000018b-35b5-d450-a3af-7dbd16990000</link><description>拜登在战争开始以来的首次采访中明确表示，找到人质是当务之急，他称哈马斯是“一群胆小鬼”，但重申需要找到一条通往巴勒斯坦国的道路</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 00:09:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/biden-as-israels-ground-invasion-looms-it-would-be-a-mistake-to-reoccupy-gaza/0000018b-35b5-d450-a3af-7dbd16990000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-16/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-35af-d051-a1cb-3dffc3c10000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 23:37:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-16/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-35af-d051-a1cb-3dffc3c10000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列人赞扬拜登时，共和党总统候选人指责他袭击哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/as-israelis-praise-biden-gop-presidential-candidates-blame-him-for-hamas-assault/0000018b-34f5-da5e-abef-bdf5eb510000</link><description>从罗恩·德桑蒂斯到妮基·哈利等共和党人指责美国总统乔·拜登向伊朗人“卑躬屈膝”，同时还批评领先者唐纳德·特朗普最近对哈马斯-以色列和“非常聪明”的真主党的评论</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 21:07:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/as-israelis-praise-biden-gop-presidential-candidates-blame-him-for-hamas-assault/0000018b-34f5-da5e-abef-bdf5eb510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列左翼学者呼吁政治盟友容忍哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-leftist-academics-call-out-political-allies-for-tolerating-hamas/0000018b-34f5-da5e-abef-bdf572610000</link><description>在进步派学者拒绝谴责哈马斯恐怖分子屠杀以色列人后，数十名以色列知识分子签署了一封信，强调“现在我们比以往任何时候都更需要全球左派的支持和声援，明确呼吁反对不分青红皂白的暴力”</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 20:53:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-leftist-academics-call-out-political-allies-for-tolerating-hamas/0000018b-34f5-da5e-abef-bdf572610000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼以色列人威胁、攻击为加沙受害者祈祷的左翼记者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israelis-threaten-attack-journalist-who-dedicated-a-prayer-to-gaza-victims/0000018b-3434-d450-a3af-7d3ccb9d0000</link><description>以色列·弗雷是左翼和极端正统派，他因直言不讳地批评以色列的政策而成为活动人士的目标，特别是他为加沙数百名妇女和儿童背诵犹太哀悼者的祈祷，他声称这些妇女和儿童被“屠杀”</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 19:12:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israelis-threaten-attack-journalist-who-dedicated-a-prayer-to-gaza-victims/0000018b-3434-d450-a3af-7d3ccb9d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡不会与司法政变对手领导的特别工作组合作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-ordered-boycott-of-general-picked-to-repair-southern-communities/0000018b-3469-dc80-a1ef-ffeddf670000</link><description>加沙地带附近的基础设施修复工作组由罗尼·努马少将领导，他参加了反改革示威活动，并请愿反对内塔尼亚胡联盟推行的一项法律。消息人士称，抵制努马的命令来自内塔尼亚胡的妻子萨拉</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 18:19:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-ordered-boycott-of-general-picked-to-repair-southern-communities/0000018b-3469-dc80-a1ef-ffeddf670000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙对哈马斯的地面攻势会是什么样子？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/what-will-israels-ground-offensive-in-gaza-against-hamas-look-like/0000018b-342b-d051-a1cb-3dfbe35e0000</link><description>以色列征召预备役军人的规模是四十年来前所未有的，再加上向加沙110万巴勒斯坦人发出的撤离令，表明这次地面攻势将比2005年脱离接触以来的任何一次入侵都更长、更密集。</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 17:53:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/what-will-israels-ground-offensive-in-gaza-against-hamas-look-like/0000018b-342b-d051-a1cb-3dfbe35e0000</guid></item><item><title>每个以色列人都是见证者、受害者和哀悼者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-15/ty-article/.highlight/every-israeli-is-a-witness-a-victim-and-a-mourner/0000018b-341a-d450-a3af-7d1eb9970000</link><description>丹尼尔的兄弟在袭击事件后失踪，在采访中途，他停下来问了自己一个问题：“你还好吗？”</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 17:42:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">h