eb-fffde61b0000</guid></item><item><title>马斯克的 X 和哈马斯的数字攻势：加沙是虚假信息的完美风暴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/musks-x-and-hamas-digital-offensive-gaza-is-a-perfect-storm-of-disinformation/0000018b-3331-d450-a3af-7b3d6a050000</link><description>在哈马斯和反疫苗者的帮助下，未经证实的网络攻击报告和以色列国防军背叛以色列的说法被作为伊朗影响网络的一部分排除在外</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 14:34:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/musks-x-and-hamas-digital-offensive-gaza-is-a-perfect-storm-of-disinformation/0000018b-3331-d450-a3af-7b3d6a050000</guid></item><item><title>“这场灾难证明了民主运动的重要性”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/this-catastrophe-proves-the-democracy-movements-importance/0000018b-334e-d1bc-a58b-7befc67b0000</link><description>当哈马斯上周对以色列发起攻击时，民主危机这一关注以色列、波兰和匈牙利民主威胁的新运动不得不重新考虑其在布鲁塞尔的启动活动。但在呼吁人们关注暴行和人质之后，参与者并没有回避政治</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 14:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/this-catastrophe-proves-the-democracy-movements-importance/0000018b-334e-d1bc-a58b-7befc67b0000</guid></item><item><title>美国国家安全顾问：我们从未“忽视”哈马斯对以色列的威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/u-s-national-security-advisor-we-never-took-eye-off-the-ball-on-hamas-threat-to-israel/0000018b-338d-d450-a3af-7b9d34e40000</link><description>沙利文告诉美国有线电视新闻网，以色列官员通知美国，他们周日打开了通往加沙南部的水管</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 14:07:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/u-s-national-security-advisor-we-never-took-eye-off-the-ball-on-hamas-threat-to-israel/0000018b-338d-d450-a3af-7b9d34e40000</guid></item></channel></rss>